  "plot": [
    {
      "plot_summary": "The Doctor and Romana land the TARDIS on a planet where the village folk fear the 'Three Who Rule'. Uncovering that these rulers are ancient astronauts turned vampires, the Doctor allies with locals to prevent the awakening of the King Vampire - an ancient Gallifreyan adversary. The climax sees the Doctor using a spacecraft from a castle to defeat the vampire threat, returning balance to the villagers' lives."
